## Backend API Endpoints Summary

| Module | Base Path | Methods |
|---|---|---|
| Auth | `/api/v1/auth` | POST `/login`, `/register`, `/change-password`, `/refresh-token`, `/forget-password`, `/reset-password` |
| Users | `/api/v1/users` | Standard CRUD |
| Products | `/api/v1/products` | GET, POST, GET/:id, PATCH/:id, DELETE/:id |
| Suppliers | `/api/v1/suppliers` | GET, POST, GET/:id, PATCH/:id, DELETE/:id |
| Customers | `/api/v1/customers` | GET, POST, GET/:id, PATCH/:id, DELETE/:id |
| Formulations | `/api/v1/formulations` | GET, POST, PATCH/:id, DELETE/:id |
| Sales | `/api/v1/sales` | POST, GET, GET/:billNo, POST `/return` |
| Purchases | `/api/v1/purchases` | POST, GET, GET/:id |
| Expenses | `/api/v1/expenses` | POST, GET, PATCH `/:id/approve` |
| Stock | `/api/v1/stock` | GET, GET `/returns`, POST `/return`, POST `/correction` |
| Credits | `/api/v1/credits` | POST/GET `/supplier`, PATCH `/supplier/:id/settle`, POST/GET `/customer` |
| Cash Adj. | `/api/v1/cash-adjustments` | POST, GET |
| Settings | `/api/v1/settings` | GET, PATCH |
| Barcode | `/api/v1/barcode` | TBD |
| Product Suppliers | `/api/v1/product-suppliers` | TBD |
| Product Links | `/api/v1/product-links` | TBD |
| Tickets | `/api/v1/tickets` | TBD |

